  "texts": [
    "People's beliefs are the dominant forces for sensemaking and forecasting, resulting in generally neutral or outright positive future paradigms.",
    "Uncertainties were expressed less negatively or skeptically in this context.",
    "Instead, unknowns about the trajectory of AI seem to facilitate critical thinking, asking questions and rationalizing dominant beliefs and hopes.",
    "A further noticeable result is that a significant proportion of the subset cohort participants argued that they could trust the technology because an AI-to-AI era is coming.",
    "To the participants this means that AI solutions will answer problems and threats generated by AI."
  ],
